title: Iraq Wikileaks Locations 2009
name: Iraq Wikileaks Locations 2009
description:
Data is from WarLogs.Wikileaks.org - a website which provides an easy way to search through the Iraq War Logs, which were made public by Wikileaks on 22nd October 2010. The documents are a set of over 391,000 reports which cover the war in Iraq from 2004 to 2009.
Data has been released, organized by type, category, date, number of casualties, and many other properties.
